Obavijest o deložaciji

226
00:25:21,688 --> 00:25:27,194
<i>Soon your sugar-daddies will all be gone</i>

227
00:25:28,278 --> 00:25:33,700
<i>You'll wake up some cold day
And find you're alone</i>

228
00:25:34,284 --> 00:25:40,791
<i>You'll call for me
But I'm gonna tell you, "Bye, bye, bye"</i>

229
00:25:40,916 --> 00:25:47,214
<i>When I turn around and walk away
You'll cry, cry, cry</i>

230
00:25:48,590 --> 00:25:52,135
<i>You're gonna cry, cry, cry</i>

231
00:25:52,302 --> 00:25:55,806
<i>And you'll cry alone</i>

232
00:25:55,973 --> 00:26:01,603
<i>When everyone's forgotten
And you're left on your own</i>

233
00:26:01,770 --> 00:26:07,693
<i>You're gonna cry, cry, cry</i>

234
00:26:09,778 --> 00:26:11,280
Hej.

235
00:26:11,822 --> 00:26:14,658
- Ti me mrziš?
- Ne, ne mrzim te.

236
00:26:16,118 --> 00:26:17,369
To je zlobna pjesma.

237
00:26:18,453 --> 00:26:20,080
Glupa je, eto što je, Viv.

238
00:26:21,748 --> 00:26:23,125
Da.

239
00:26:28,130 --> 00:26:31,133
Vi... Viv, to je samo pjesma.

240
00:26:35,473 --> 00:26:37,100
RABLJENI AUTI

241
00:26:38,684 --> 00:26:39,977
Tonski studio

242
00:26:48,778 --> 00:26:51,364
Oprostite?
Jeste li vi vlasnik?

243
00:26:51,614 --> 00:26:54,409
- Jesam.
- Ja sam J.R. Cash.

244
00:26:54,617 --> 00:26:55,868
Sam Phillips.

245
00:26:56,119 --> 00:26:59,038
Drago mi je.
Pjevac sam, imam i sastav.

246
00:26:59,330 --> 00:27:00,790
Radili smo na nekim
pjesmama.

247
00:27:01,040 --> 00:27:02,959
Ako želite snimiti plocu,
to stoji 4 $.

248
00:27:03,251 --> 00:27:06,379
A ovi decki na slikama na zidu?

249
00:27:06,629 --> 00:27:09,674
- I oni placaju cetiri dolara?
- Oni su na mojoj etiketi.

250
00:27:09,882 --> 00:27:11,717
Kako da ja doðem tamo?

251
00:27:11,926 --> 00:27:13,928
- Idete na audiciju.
- Odmah?

252
00:27:14,178 --> 00:27:15,972
Ne...

253
00:27:16,222 --> 00:27:18,349
Nazovite moju tajnicu, Marion.

254
00:27:18,641 --> 00:27:21,436
Zakazat ce vam sastanak
za sljedeci mjesec.

255
00:27:21,728 --> 00:27:24,981
- Ne mogu toliko cekati.
- Molim?

256
00:27:26,190 --> 00:27:27,900
Ne mogu toliko cekati.

257
00:27:31,237 --> 00:27:34,282
- A ova? Izglacat cu je.
- Ne.

258
00:27:34,532 --> 00:27:37,201
Johne, ne možeš tu nositi.
Crna je.

259
00:27:37,452 --> 00:27:40,580
To je jedina boja košulje
koju svi imamo. Ništa ne fali.

260
00:27:40,830 --> 00:27:44,292
- Kao da ideš na sprovod.
- Pa, možda i idem.

261
00:27:45,168 --> 00:27:48,921
- Da, znam kad me Isus spasio
- Spasio je dušu moju

262
00:27:49,213 --> 00:27:52,925
- Onoga trena kad mi je On oprostio
- Iscijelio me

263
00:27:53,176 --> 00:27:59,640
Skinuo je moje teško breme
Gospod mi je podario mir u srcu

264
00:27:59,932 --> 00:28:00,933
Mir u srcu

265
00:28:01,184 --> 00:28:04,520
Sotona me nece navesti
Da u to posumnjam

266
00:28:04,729 --> 00:28:07,690
- Necu posumnjati
- Ja cu to klicati

267
00:28:07,899 --> 00:28:09,025
Ja cu to klicati

268
00:28:09,275 --> 00:28:10,318
Pa, bio sam ondje...

269
00:28:10,610 --> 00:28:14,947
cekajte. Žao mi je što prekidam,
ali imate li što drugo?

270
00:28:19,243 --> 00:28:22,955
Žao mi je. Ne mogu više
izdavati crkveno pjevanje.

271
00:28:26,209 --> 00:28:27,877
I to je to?

272
00:28:29,462 --> 00:28:32,715
Ne izdajem materijal
koji se nece prodavati, g. Cash.

273
00:28:33,007 --> 00:28:35,510
A ovakvo se crkveno pjevanje
nece prodavati.

274
00:28:36,677 --> 00:28:38,888
Radi li se o crkvenom izboru
ili mom pjevanju?

275
00:28:39,347 --> 00:28:40,932
Oboje.

276
00:28:41,390 --> 00:28:43,935
Što fali mome pjevanju?

277
00:28:44,227 --> 00:28:45,561
Ne vjerujem vam.

278
00:28:46,896 --> 00:28:51,067
- Kažete da ne vjerujem u Boga?
- Daj, idemo.

279
00:28:51,401 --> 00:28:54,362
Ne. Želim shvatiti.
Došli smo, svirali...

280
00:28:54,570 --> 00:28:56,906
...i on mi kaže
da ne vjerujem u Boga.

281
00:28:57,156 --> 00:29:01,953
Znate što vam govorim.
culi smo vec tu pjesmu.

282
00:29:02,703 --> 00:29:07,875
Tisucu puta. Baš takvu
kakvu ste sad otpjevali.

283
00:29:08,835 --> 00:29:12,004
- Niste nam objasnili.
- Objasnio?

284
00:29:12,255 --> 00:29:16,509
Da vam objasnim?
U redu, evo ga.

285
00:29:17,635 --> 00:29:21,097
Udari vas kamion,
ležite uz cestu i umirete.

286
00:29:21,347 --> 00:29:24,475
Imate vremena otpjevati
samo jednu pjesmu.

287
00:29:24,725 --> 00:29:28,312
Jednu pjesmu koju bi ljudi
zapamtili prije nego umrete.

288
00:29:28,563 --> 00:29:32,900
Jednu pjesmu da Bogu kažete
što osjecate o svome životu...

289
00:29:33,192 --> 00:29:36,237
...na Zemlji, jednu pjesmu
koja bi vas opisala.

290
00:29:36,446 --> 00:29:38,865
Hocete mi reci
da je to ta pjesma?

291
00:29:39,115 --> 00:29:43,578
Pjesma Jimmieja Davisa
koju stalno slušamo na radiju?

292
00:29:44,328 --> 00:29:47,039
O unutarnjem miru
i kako je stvaran...

293
00:29:47,290 --> 00:29:49,751
...i kako cete to propovijedati?

294
00:29:50,001 --> 00:29:53,087
Ili biste otpjevali nešto drugo?

295
00:29:53,337 --> 00:29:55,506
Nešto stvarno?
Nešto što osjecate?

296
00:29:55,715 --> 00:29:58,134
Odmah vam kažem,
takve pjesme...

297
00:29:58,384 --> 00:30:00,720
...ljudi žele slušati.
Takve pjesme...

298
00:30:00,970 --> 00:30:03,473
...doista spašavaju ljude.

299
00:30:04,432 --> 00:30:07,852
Nema to veze
s vjerovanjem u Boga, g. Cash.

300
00:30:08,061 --> 00:30:10,772
To ima veze
s vjerovanjem u sebe.

301
00:30:16,611 --> 00:30:19,655
Imam nekoliko pjesama
koje sam napisao u Zrakoplovstvu.

302
00:30:22,283 --> 00:30:24,577
Imate li što protiv
Zrakoplovstva?

303
00:30:25,536 --> 00:30:26,913
Nemam.

304
00:30:28,748 --> 00:30:30,541
Ja imam.

305
00:30:33,795 --> 00:30:36,923
Što god sad zasviraš,
mi to ne znamo.

306
00:30:40,134 --> 00:30:43,387
cujem, stiže vlak

307
00:30:44,347 --> 00:30:47,558
Skrece iza zavoja

308
00:30:48,351 --> 00:30:51,938
Nisam vidio sunca

309
00:30:52,397 --> 00:30:55,400
Ne znam otkada

310
00:30:56,359 --> 00:31:00,363
camim u Folsom-zatvoru

311
00:31:01,531 --> 00:31:05,993
A vrijeme se vuce

312
00:31:12,041 --> 00:31:16,379
Al' vlak taj ide dalje

313
00:31:17,505 --> 00:31:22,051
Na jug u San Antone

314
00:31:24,220 --> 00:31:27,265
Kad sam bio dijete

315
00:31:27,849 --> 00:31:31,018
Mama mi je rekla: "Sine

316
00:31:31,894 --> 00:31:37,859
Uvijek budi dobar djecak
Nikada se ne igraj oružjem"

317
00:31:38,109 --> 00:31:41,904
A ja sam u Renu ubio covjeka

318
00:31:42,864 --> 00:31:46,659
Tek tako da vidim da umire

319
00:31:50,788 --> 00:31:54,041
Kada cujem zviždaljke zov

320
00:31:54,792 --> 00:31:58,504
Objesim glavu i placem

321
00:31:59,714 --> 00:32:04,927
Kladim se, bogataši jedu
U raskošnim kolima za rucavanje

322
00:32:05,136 --> 00:32:10,016
Vjerojatno piju kavu
I puše krupne cigare

323
00:32:10,224 --> 00:32:13,102
E pa, znao sam što me ceka

324
00:32:13,936 --> 00:32:17,315
Znam, ne mogu biti slobodan

325
00:32:20,693 --> 00:32:23,696
A ti ljudi se stalno micu

326
00:32:24,322 --> 00:32:27,992
I mene to izjeda

327
00:33:01,275 --> 00:33:02,985
Gdje si bio?

328
00:33:04,362 --> 00:33:05,988
Jesi li pijan?

329
00:33:09,617 --> 00:33:13,663
- Što se dogodilo?
- Nije mu se svidio naš crkveni izbor.

330
00:33:15,123 --> 00:33:17,417
Pa sam mu odsvirao
pjesmu koju sam napisao.

331
00:33:18,793 --> 00:33:21,212
Snimili smo plocu, Viv.

332
00:33:21,421 --> 00:33:23,714
Pravu plocu.

333
00:33:28,344 --> 00:33:32,557
Šest smo je puta odsvirali.
Morao sam je stalno pjevati.

334
00:33:32,807 --> 00:33:36,227
Trebala si vidjeti Marshalla,
bio je tako nervozan.

335
00:33:36,519 --> 00:33:38,730
Ali, snimili smo moju pjesmu.

336
00:33:40,148 --> 00:33:41,649
- Isuse!
- Ne mogu vjerovati.

337
00:33:46,985 --> 00:33:50,155
<i>Da, gospodo, slušate
Tennessee Farm Hour.</i>

338
00:33:50,322 --> 00:33:53,700
Evo jedne nove
od naše Patsy.

339
00:34:05,629 --> 00:34:06,922
Dobar tekst.

340
00:34:07,256 --> 00:34:08,632
Jeste to vi napisali?

341
00:34:08,841 --> 00:34:11,260
<i>Da, dobio je nagradu za pjesništvo
u "Stars and Stripes".</i>

342
00:34:11,510 --> 00:34:14,429
To je bilo prije...
To je bilo prije nego sam ga uglazbio.

343
00:34:22,563 --> 00:34:24,356
Hej, okreni to umjesto mene, hoceš?

344
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:32,156
<i>Ovo je Bob Neal, a vi slušate
Tennessee Farm Hour...</i>

345
00:34:32,364 --> 00:34:34,449
...omoguceno od
Bronson Seed and Feed.

346
00:34:36,410 --> 00:34:39,621
G. Phillips? O, covjece, slomio sam je.
Slomio sam je, slomio sam je.

347
00:34:39,830 --> 00:34:42,833
John. John. Što si slomio?
- Plocu, covjece, slomljena je.

348
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:44,710
G. Neal, zamolio me je da je okrenem...

349
00:34:44,835 --> 00:34:47,963
...i kad sam krenuo,
ispala mi je iz ruku i slomila se.

350
00:34:48,130 --> 00:34:50,549
Najgore je, mislim da mu se svidjela.

351
00:34:50,716 --> 00:34:52,885
John, znam.
Možemo to uraditi odmah.

352
00:34:53,051 --> 00:34:55,929
- Hajdemo dovesti Luthera i Marshalla.
- Ne moramo to snimiti. Sjedni.

353
00:34:56,054 --> 00:34:57,222
- Hocu da je snimim.
- John.

354
00:34:57,431 --> 00:35:01,143
Sjedni, John.
Ne moraš snimiti još jednu.

355
00:35:01,310 --> 00:35:02,936
To što si slomio je probni uzorak.

356
00:35:03,103 --> 00:35:07,482
Tvornica mi šalje jednu takvu
prije nego otiskaju tisucu u seriji.

357
00:35:09,484 --> 00:35:11,862
Zajebava vas, G. Phillips.

358
00:35:12,070 --> 00:35:13,864
Nema šanse, nitko ne bi bio
toliko glup.

359
00:35:14,031 --> 00:35:15,491
Pusti ga, Jerry Lee.

360
00:35:24,500 --> 00:35:26,960
John?
Hmm?

361
00:35:28,212 --> 00:35:30,672
Kada ceš pricati...

362
00:35:30,839 --> 00:35:33,592
...kako bi ova tura uspjela?

363
00:35:34,301 --> 00:35:36,011
Zato jer si...

364
00:35:36,220 --> 00:35:41,350
...tri od cetiri tjedna van grada
sljedeca tri mjeseca.

365
00:35:42,559 --> 00:35:44,144
Pa...

366
00:35:46,271 --> 00:35:48,565
Htio si to.
- Viv, ne mogu vjerovati.

367
00:35:48,732 --> 00:35:50,275
Opet to svira.

368
00:35:50,442 --> 00:35:52,069
<i>Them folks at Sun tell me...</i>

369
00:35:52,194 --> 00:35:54,780
<i>... this boy starts a
four-state tour next week.</i>

370
00:35:58,659 --> 00:36:00,744
