Na klaviru cu ovom svirati
Mali boogie!

381
00:36:59,217 --> 00:37:01,887
Sjajno ce vam biti
Drmat cete se

382
00:37:02,095 --> 00:37:04,765
Necete moci prestati
Sve dok ne puknete

383
00:37:04,973 --> 00:37:07,309
Zove se Lewisov Boogie
Na Lewisov nacin

384
00:37:07,601 --> 00:37:11,563
Gospodine, svaki dan plešem svoj
