385
00:37:16,234 --> 00:37:18,904
Nikad nisam vidio
da netko tako svira.

386
00:37:26,411 --> 00:37:29,081
A u New Orleansu

387
00:37:29,331 --> 00:37:31,958
U zemlji snova
Najboljem prokletom mjestu

388
00:37:32,167 --> 00:37:34,461
Koje vidjeli ste ikad
Macke divljaju

389
00:37:34,753 --> 00:37:37,714
Pleši boogie strastveni
