390
00:37:38,006 --> 00:37:40,008
I udariš!
Zove se Lewisov Boogie

391
00:37:40,258 --> 00:37:41,885
Na Lewisov nacin

392
00:37:42,219 --> 00:37:47,516
Svaki dan plešem svoj mali boogie!

393
00:37:49,434 --> 00:37:54,648
Jerry Lee Lewis,
dame i gospodo! "Ubojica"!

394
00:37:56,066 --> 00:37:58,443
Pripremite si lijesove, decki.

395
00:37:58,652 --> 00:38:00,654
Nitko ne svira poslije
"Ubojice".

396
00:38:00,904 --> 00:38:05,158
Sljedeci momci
snimili su prvu plocu "Cry, cry, cry".

397
00:38:05,409 --> 00:38:07,703
Dovraga! Sad i kasnim.

398
00:38:07,911 --> 00:38:09,955
Ajme! Oprostite.

399
00:38:10,247 --> 00:38:13,875
Moj je red. O, ne.
Zaplela mi se haljina.

400
00:38:14,167 --> 00:38:18,296
- Hej, Bille! Pricekaj, Bille. Dolazim.
- Mislim...

401
00:38:18,505 --> 00:38:22,050
Mislim da sam cuo glas
June Carter, dame i gospodo.

402
00:38:24,469 --> 00:38:27,139
Odmah cu, Bille!

403
00:38:27,389 --> 00:38:29,307
Znaš li kad, June?

404
00:38:29,975 --> 00:38:32,769
Pa, Bille, zaplela sam se!

405
00:38:33,478 --> 00:38:37,691
- U što, June srce?
- Gitaru Johnnyja Casha.

406
00:38:39,067 --> 00:38:42,029
Ne brini, ovo ce biti smiješno
dvije minute.

407
00:38:42,320 --> 00:38:45,574
