Zaigraj u cipelama
Zapleši

434
00:40:41,690 --> 00:40:45,527
Uhvati ritam kada te depra hvata

435
00:40:46,945 --> 00:40:49,614
cistac cipela nikada ne pada u depru

436
00:40:49,823 --> 00:40:51,491
A radi najprljaviji posao
U gradu

437
00:40:51,700 --> 00:40:55,746
Sagiba se nam tuðim nogama
Na vjetrovitome kutu prljave ulice

438
00:40:55,996 --> 00:40:57,914
