00:41:04,504 --> 00:41:08,467
"Uhvati ritam kada te depra hvata

443
00:41:08,717 --> 00:41:13,430
Daj, uhvati ritam kada te depra hvata

444
00:41:13,680 --> 00:41:15,599
Da, skokovit ritam
Daje ti osjecaj lijep

445
00:41:15,891 --> 00:41:18,352
Sve ce jade stresti
Iz tvog uma zabrinutog

446
00:41:18,602 --> 00:41:22,189
Uhvati ritam kada te depra hvata"

447
00:41:39,206 --> 00:41:40,666
To!

448
00:41:41,917 --> 00:41:44,086
Sjeo sam da slušam cistaca cipela

449
00:41:44,336 --> 00:41:46,463
Mislio sam da cu skociti od radosti

450
00:41:46,672 --> 00:41:48,548
Nanosio je laštilo na cipelu
Lijevo i desno

451
00:41:48,757 --> 00:41:50,842
Uhvatio krpu za laštenje
I cvrsto je stegnuo

452
00:41:51,093 --> 00:41:52,803
Jedanput je zastao
Da obriše znoj

453
00:41:53,053 --> 00:41:55,472
Rekao sam:
"Premalen si djecak za takav posao"

454
00:41:55,764 --> 00:41:57,265
Rekao je: "Sviða mi se"
Uz širok, širok osmijeh

455
00:41:57,516 --> 00:41:59,142
Nastavio je laštiti
Pa opet rekao:

456
00:41:59,393 --> 00:42:03,063
"Uhvati ritam kad te depra hvata

457
00:42:03,313 --> 00:42:04,439
Daj!
Uhvati ritam

458
00:42:06,024 --> 00:42:08,110
Kad te depra hvata

459
00:42:08,402 --> 00:42:10,654
Stoji samo deset centa
Svaka cipela pet centa

460
00:42:10,946 --> 00:42:12,990
A vama ce to vrijediti milijun dolara

461
00:42:13,198 --> 00:42:18,412
Uhvati ritam kad te depra hvata"

462
00:42:24,167 --> 00:42:27,754
Hvala! Hvala najljepša!

463
00:42:28,046 --> 00:42:29,756
Volim tu kosu, dugu i crnu

464
00:42:30,007 --> 00:42:31,800
Visi ti po sredini leða

465
00:42:32,050 --> 00:42:35,679
Nemoj se ošišati, ma što radila
Treba mi da kroz nju provlacim prste

466
00:42:35,971 --> 00:42:39,266
Viv, kažem ti,
ovo je najbolji nastup ikad.

467
00:42:39,558 --> 00:42:42,561
cak i najbolji nastup
koji sam ikad vidio, bez šale.

468
00:42:42,769 --> 00:42:46,314
- Gdje si?
- Texarkana. Nedostaješ mi.

469
00:42:46,648 --> 00:42:50,193
Hej, jesi cula Orbisonovu novu pjesmu?
Sad je dvokorak, slušaj.

470
00:43:06,679 --> 00:43:08,223
- cuješ?
- Dovraga.

471
00:43:08,256 --> 00:43:09,299
Što je?

472
00:43:09,349 --> 00:43:12,811
Dovraga. Roseanne
se udarila o stol.

473
00:43:12,861 --> 00:43:16,031
Roseanne. Evo ti tate.

474
00:43:16,281 --> 00:43:18,617
Hej, Roseanne? Tata je.

475
00:43:18,867 --> 00:43:22,579
Dušo, nemoj plakati.
Tata ce brzo doci kuci.

476
00:43:22,871 --> 00:43:24,331
Johne, moram ici.

477
00:43:24,623 --> 00:43:26,375
Moram ici, Johne.

478
00:43:27,292 --> 00:43:28,919
Bok.

479
00:43:35,365 --> 00:43:38,785
Hej, svi pozdravite Johnnyja Casha.
Tata, on je napisao tu "Cry, Cry, Cry" pjesmu.

480
00:43:38,994 --> 00:43:40,204
Mama Maybelle.

481
00:43:40,370 --> 00:43:43,415
- Kako si, Johnny Cash?
- Dobro. Ma što, odlicno sam, g'ðo.

482
00:43:43,624 --> 00:43:45,709
- Bok, John, ja sam Ezra.
- Da, znam.

483
00:43:46,585 --> 00:43:50,005
- Drago mi je što sam te sreo, sine.
- I meni je drago, gospodine.

484
00:44:12,695 --> 00:44:15,906
Neki dan sam ušla u gostionicu s plesom

485
00:44:16,157 --> 00:44:19,785
Ubacila pet centa u džuboks
Tek tako da cujem kako svira

486
00:44:20,077 --> 00:44:23,831
Nije mi na umu bio nijedan napjev
Nisam pricekala da biram

487
00:44:24,457 --> 00:44:28,502
Samo sam ubacila pet centi u otvor
I svirala Džuboks Bluz

488
00:44:36,552 --> 00:44:38,512
<i>There's a guy in there
With an old tin horn</i>

489
00:44:38,720 --> 00:44:40,514
<i>And a feller on an old banjo</i>

490
00:44:40,681 --> 00:44:42,766
<i>And the man on the fiddle
He wasn't no slouch</i>

491
00:44:42,933 --> 00:44:45,102
<i>He could really drag that bow</i>

492
00:44:48,306 --> 00:44:50,892
Dobro si zvucao veceras, Cash.
Sjajno.

493
00:44:51,100 --> 00:44:53,227
Hvala ti.

494
00:44:54,187 --> 00:44:55,938
Hoceš krumpirice s cilijem?

495
00:44:56,189 --> 00:44:58,274
Ne, hvala.

496
00:44:58,566 --> 00:45:02,487
Pred reflektorima je bila
dok smo ti i ja još grizli nožne prste.

497
00:45:02,987 --> 00:45:05,156
Kažu da je Maybelle
imala jasle u Rymanu...

498
00:45:05,364 --> 00:45:07,992
...kako bi je izvadili
da urla i zavija...

499
00:45:08,201 --> 00:45:09,952
...a zatim je vratili
na spavanje.

500
00:45:10,836 --> 00:45:12,379
<i>It must have been a drum</i>

501
00:45:12,796 --> 00:45:16,884
<i>It gave that song a solid beat
Boy, he was goin' some</i>

502
00:45:24,516 --> 00:45:28,395
<i>I walked into a honky-tonky
Just the other day</i>

503
00:45:28,604 --> 00:45:32,232
<i>I dropped a nickel in a jukebox
Just to hear it play</i>

504
00:45:32,649 --> 00:45:36,570
<i>I didn't have no tune in mind
I didn't wait to choose</i>

505
00:45:36,737 --> 00:45:40,574
<i>Just dropped a nickel in the slot
And played the Jukebox Blues</i>

506
00:45:48,665 --> 00:45:52,461
<i>I've played a lot of jukeboxes
Most every one in town</i>

507
00:45:52,669 --> 00:45:56,965
<i>But that's the first tune I ever heard
That could make one dance around</i>

508
00:45:58,926 --> 00:46:00,761
<i>Play the Jukebox Blues</i>

509
00:46:00,969 --> 00:46:04,890
<i>Such a rhythm I never heard
I danced out both of my shoes</i>

510
00:46:12,760 --> 00:46:14,261
HOT PIT BAR-B-Q
RESTORAN

511
00:46:15,971 --> 00:46:18,933
- Odlazimo za sat vremena.
- U redu.

512
00:46:21,227 --> 00:46:24,188
To je lijepa prica, dušo.

513
00:46:25,022 --> 00:46:26,690
U redu.

514
00:46:26,941 --> 00:46:28,400
Ne.

515
00:46:29,693 --> 00:46:31,237
Odlazim za pet minuta.

516
00:46:32,279 --> 00:46:33,572
U redu.

517
00:46:33,864 --> 00:46:36,033
Je li sve drugo u redu?

518
00:46:37,618 --> 00:46:39,078
I ja tebe volim.

519
00:46:40,955 --> 00:46:43,499
- Bok.
- Kako ste?

520
00:46:43,749 --> 00:46:45,459
- Kavu?
- Može.

521
00:46:45,751 --> 00:46:47,503
I tost, molim vas.

522
00:46:51,632 --> 00:46:53,259
- Hej.
- Hej, kako si?

523
00:46:53,467 --> 00:46:54,718
Dobro. Mogu?

524
00:46:54,969 --> 00:46:56,387
Svakako.

525
00:46:56,637 --> 00:46:58,973
- Jesi li izgubila glas?
- Jesam.

526
00:46:59,265 --> 00:47:01,058
Namucila sam se veceras.

527
00:47:01,559 --> 00:47:05,146
Moram te pitati
kao uspijevaš dobiti taj zvuk.

528
00:47:05,479 --> 00:47:06,480
Koji zvuk?

529
00:47:06,689 --> 00:47:10,609
Z vuk o kojem svi pricaju.
Miran kao vlak. Oštar kao žilet.

530
00:47:11,944 --> 00:47:15,114
Svirali bi brže da možemo.

531
00:47:15,364 --> 00:47:18,701
Izgleda da tako izaðe iz mene.

532
00:47:19,618 --> 00:47:22,329
- Moram zatvoriti blagajnu.
- Svakako.

533
00:47:24,623 --> 00:47:26,333
Hvala.

534
00:47:28,210 --> 00:47:30,921
Ovo je slika moje žene, Viv.

535
00:47:31,130 --> 00:47:34,508
- Moja curica, Roseanne.
- Vidi je. Preslatka je.

536
00:47:35,342 --> 00:47:37,011
Hvala. Drugo dijete
je na putu.

537
00:47:37,219 --> 00:47:38,637
- I ja imam curicu.
- Da?

538
00:47:38,929 --> 00:47:41,724
Zove se Carlene. Da.
Vršnjakinje su.

539
00:47:45,770 --> 00:47:48,773
Kad sam služio u vojsci,
gledao sam tvoje slike.

540
00:47:49,064 --> 00:47:51,150
Znaš, iz casopisa.

541
00:47:53,444 --> 00:47:55,863
Ne, nije bilo tako.

542
00:47:56,113 --> 00:47:58,365
Sviðala mi se tvoja glazba.

543
00:47:58,574 --> 00:48:00,117
- Da?
- Da.

544
00:48:00,409 --> 00:48:04,288
Bila si... Još uvijek si...
Hocu reci... Pratim te.

545
00:48:04,580 --> 00:48:06,791
Da, tebe i tvoju obitelj.

546
00:48:07,041 --> 00:48:09,585
Cijeli život slušam tvoj glas.

547
00:48:10,920 --> 00:48:14,840
Ja i moj brat Jack
smo uvijek slušali tvoje pjesme.

548
00:48:15,091 --> 00:48:17,009
- Poput "Swallerin' Place".
- Da.

549
00:48:17,259 --> 00:48:20,429
Voljeli smo kad si ju sama pjevala.

550
00:48:20,721 --> 00:48:23,516
Ti i Jack ste jedini.

551
00:48:24,475 --> 00:48:28,187
- Kako to misliš?
- Nisam bogzna kakva pjevacica.

552
00:48:28,437 --> 00:48:32,191
Imam osobnost, drskost.

553
00:48:32,441 --> 00:48:36,403
Sve dajem, ali moja sestra Anita
je ta koja ima glas.

554
00:48:36,779 --> 00:48:38,447
- Tko to kaže?
- Svi.

555
00:48:38,697 --> 00:48:40,324
Moja mama, moj tata.

556
00:48:40,574 --> 00:48:44,662
Tako sam i naucila biti smiješna.
Da mogu nešto ponuditi.

557
00:48:46,997 --> 00:48:48,833
Pa...

558
00:48:49,291 --> 00:48:51,502
Roditelji nisu uvijek
najbolji u procjeni...

559
00:48:51,752 --> 00:48:53,421
...ako mene pitaš.

560
00:48:57,550 --> 00:48:59,885
Koliko si dugo na turneji?

561
00:49:00,136 --> 00:49:03,055
Još par tjedana.
Tek smo krenuli...

562
00:49:03,305 --> 00:49:06,642
...ali osjecam da vec dugo traje.

563
00:49:06,851 --> 00:49:08,310
U to sam sigurna.

564
00:49:08,602 --> 00:49:10,396
Idem.
Idemo do Rymana.

565
00:49:10,688 --> 00:49:13,399
Reci Jacku da upali radio,
otpjevat cu mu nešto.

566
00:49:13,691 --> 00:49:14,900
Što mu se sviða?

567
00:49:15,151 --> 00:49:19,363
Lijepo od tebe.
Ali, on je umro.

568
00:49:19,613 --> 00:49:22,658
Žao mi je.
Jeste li bili bliski?

569
00:49:23,325 --> 00:49:27,580
Da, jesmo. On...

570
00:49:31,333 --> 00:49:36,130
Smiješno je to, dugo nisam
govorio o Jacku.

571
00:49:37,673 --> 00:49:42,136
Kad je umro,
stalno sam govorio o njemu, ali...

572
00:49:44,221 --> 00:49:47,099
...ljudima je dosadilo slušati.

573
00:49:47,808 --> 00:49:49,685
Pa sam prestao.

574
00:49:56,233 --> 00:49:57,568
Johne?

575
00:50:01,822 --> 00:50:03,699
Umoran si, zar ne?

576
00:50:06,160 --> 00:50:07,912
Jesam.

577
00:50:08,746 --> 00:50:10,873
Usporit ce se.

578
00:50:12,917 --> 00:50:14,502
Hoce.

579
00:50:15,544 --> 00:50:17,922
Idem ja.

580
00:50:18,839 --> 00:50:20,049
Bilo mi je drago.

581
00:50:20,299 --> 00:50:21,801
- I meni.
- cuvaj se.

582
00:50:22,009 --> 00:50:25,054
- Uskoro se vidimo.
- Slušaj radio.

583
00:50:25,304 --> 00:50:28,682
- Otpjevat cu ti "Swallerin' Place".
- Hocu.

584
00:50:28,974 --> 00:50:30,601
U redu.

585
00:50:43,322 --> 00:50:45,032
U redu je. Dobro je.

586
00:50:45,407 --> 00:50:46,867
U redu, gospoðo.

587
00:50:49,745 --> 00:50:52,540
Kad si ga posljednji put
cula da se mice?

588
00:50:52,748 --> 00:50:54,667
Ne znam.

589
00:51:03,968 --> 00:51:06,971
Mislila sam da ceš mi
danas pomoci, Johne.

590
00:51:13,769 --> 00:51:15,938
Sutra ideš.

591
00:51:16,230 --> 00:51:18,607
- Da.
- Da.

592
00:51:19,233 --> 00:51:23,237
Pocni živjeti život ovdje
kad si tu...

593
00:51:23,487 --> 00:51:25,531
...prije nego što
opet moraš otici.

594
00:51:27,867 --> 00:51:30,786
Razmišljao sam.

595
00:51:31,078 --> 00:51:33,706
Možda bi Bob mogao
pogurati datume.

596
00:51:34,331 --> 00:51:36,625
Sretan sam kad sam ovdje.

597
00:51:38,335 --> 00:51:41,130
Volim se buditi i ugledati tebe.

598
00:51:52,183 --> 00:51:53,642
One torbe tamo...

599
00:51:55,019 --> 00:51:58,939
Ta pisma su uglavnom od djevojaka.

600
00:51:59,273 --> 00:52:03,235
Devet od deset.
I vecina su nepristojna.

601
00:52:03,486 --> 00:52:07,072
Reba je htjela odgovoriti na par njih.
Polovica njih nema ni 15 godina.

602
00:52:07,364 --> 00:52:10,826
A šalju slike sebe
u kupacim kostimima.

603
00:52:11,076 --> 00:52:14,538
Slike za tebe dok si u Folsomu.

604
00:52:16,999 --> 00:52:19,835
- Viv.
- Jedna ti je poslala svoj dnevnik...

605
00:52:20,086 --> 00:52:22,129
Viv, nemoj to citati.

606
00:52:22,379 --> 00:52:24,840
Trenutno je ludnica,
to je sve.

607
00:52:25,174 --> 00:52:26,759
Znaš.

608
00:52:27,426 --> 00:52:29,804
Trebala si vidjeti
kako je bilo prošli tjedan.

609
00:52:30,054 --> 00:52:32,473
Bili smo na sajmu...

610
00:52:32,723 --> 00:52:35,309
...autobus pun
mladih djevojaka je stao...

611
00:52:35,518 --> 00:52:37,436
...i sve jurnu iz njega van.

612
00:52:37,686 --> 00:52:40,606
I potrce vrišteci
prema Carlu i Royu.

613
00:52:40,898 --> 00:52:43,984
Johne, složenac me ceka
u pecnici, tvoja sestra je...

614
00:52:44,276 --> 00:52:47,655
...u kuhinji i ne želim
razgovarati o turneji.

615
00:52:49,115 --> 00:52:52,034
Viv, ti si je prva spomenula.

616
00:52:52,952 --> 00:52:55,204
Zapravo, to je moje novo pravilo.

617
00:52:55,454 --> 00:52:56,747
Kad doðeš kuci...

618
00:52:56,997 --> 00:52:59,917
...želim razgovarati
o obicnim stvarima.

619
00:53:00,167 --> 00:53:02,128
Viv, nemoj mi
odreðivati pravila.

620
00:53:02,420 --> 00:53:04,171
Imam samo pravila.

621
00:53:04,422 --> 00:53:06,549
Ovdje sam, sad.

622
00:53:06,841 --> 00:53:07,925
Pokušavam
ici tamo...

623
00:53:08,134 --> 00:53:10,553
...i biti ovdje
s tobom i djecom.

624
00:53:10,845 --> 00:53:13,347
I pisati pjesme.
Što hoceš od mene?

625
00:53:13,597 --> 00:53:17,226
Kupio sam ti kucu iz snova.
Imaš lijepe stvari.

626
00:53:17,476 --> 00:53:20,229
Imaš auto.
Što hoceš od mene?

627
00:53:20,521 --> 00:53:26,360
Želim tebe, Johne. Tebe!
I sve što si mi obecao.

628
00:53:27,486 --> 00:53:29,655
Što ako ne mogu?

629
00:53:38,747 --> 00:53:42,042
Zajednicka turneja, 1956.

630
00:53:57,850 --> 00:53:59,435
Razmišljaš o necemu?

631
00:54:01,604 --> 00:54:03,314
Što radiš, covjece?

632
00:54:03,606 --> 00:54:05,983
Izraðujem bombu.

633
00:54:06,192 --> 00:54:08,569
Kamo opet idemo?

634
00:54:08,819 --> 00:54:11,781
Tyler. Šou Georgea Jonesa.

635
00:54:12,156 --> 00:54:14,825
A gdje smo bili?

636
00:54:15,117 --> 00:54:17,745
- Evo ti još jedna, Carl.
- U Austinu, Carl.

637
00:54:17,995 --> 00:54:19,538
Tamo ste me pokupili.

638
00:54:19,789 --> 00:54:21,957
Hej, Johne,
jesi li vidio novu top-listu?

639
00:54:22,249 --> 00:54:23,959
"Cry, cry, cry"
je na 14. mjestu.

640
00:54:24,251 --> 00:54:26,295
cuo sam,
ali nisam vidio.

641
00:54:26,545 --> 00:54:30,007
Gdje god bili, znam kamo idemo.

642
00:54:31,467 --> 00:54:34,512
Svi u ovome autu
idu ravno u pakao.

643
00:54:34,720 --> 00:54:37,139
A onaj auto tamo?

644
00:54:37,431 --> 00:54:40,142
Svi idemo u pakao
zbog pjesama koje pjevamo.

645
00:54:40,476 --> 00:54:42,561
Ljudi koji ih slušaju
otici ce u pakao.

646
00:54:42,770 --> 00:54:44,688
Zacepi s time.

647
00:54:44,939 --> 00:54:46,732
Bog nam je dao
veliku jabuku.

648
00:54:46,941 --> 00:54:48,359
Rekao je:
"Nemojte ju dirati."

649
00:54:48,692 --> 00:54:52,238
Nije rekao "dirnite je s tu i tamo
ili gricnite kad ogladnite".

650
00:54:52,530 --> 00:54:54,365
Rekao je:
"Nemojte ju dirati."

651
00:54:54,949 --> 00:54:56,659
Ne razmišljajte
da je dirate.

652
00:54:56,951 --> 00:54:58,327
Ne pjevajte
da je dirate.

653
00:54:58,577 --> 00:55:01,413
Ne pomišljajte pjevati
o tome da je dirate.

654
00:55:04,792 --> 00:55:08,546
A ja, Jerry Lee?
Idem li i ja u pakao?

655
00:55:09,755 --> 00:55:12,341
Ne, June. Ti si prekrasna.

656
00:55:13,175 --> 00:55:16,095
Pospana sam.

657
00:55:18,722 --> 00:55:21,016
Zaljubit cu se u nju.

658
00:55:25,146 --> 00:55:27,481
Osjeti mi srce.
Doði. Ozbiljno.

659
00:55:27,773 --> 00:55:30,484
Osjeti ga.
Kuca samo za tebe.

660
00:55:30,651 --> 00:55:31,861
- Prestani.
- Daj, osjeti ga.

661
00:55:32,111 --> 00:55:33,446
- Zaljubljujem se u tebe.
- Hej.

